data.description: Welcome home to this spacious pool home in the quiet neighborhood of Sherwood Villas in Titusville. This home features 3 bedrooms, an office (no closet), and a large bonus room, which can be used as flex space or a 4th bedroom. The kitchen has a stainless steel range and dishwasher. The home also offers an oversized great room with a wood-burning fire place, as well as a separate dining room. The great room boasts a beautiful cedar ceiling. The pool includes a screened enclosure as well as some covered space. So many recent improvements including new roof in 2021, AC - 2019, pool re-surfaced in 2023, new vinyl siding in 2022, hurricane impact garage door and new opener in 2023, gutters in 2022.
